# Buttons (Button_v2)

**Scope:** This rule is not tied to all TSX files—only auto-includes when `Button.tsx` is in context. For `<button>` / CTA work in other files (e.g. `PageLevelMenu`, pages), attach **`@buttons`** or this rule in chat.

All buttons: `rounded-[8px] font-semibold transition-colors`, centered text+icon layout.

## Props
- `emphasis`: High | Medium | Low
- `size`: Large | Medium | Small
- `icon`: None | Leading | Trailing | Both | Only
- `state`: Normal | Hover | Loading
- `enabled`: boolean

## Emphasis Levels

### High (Primary)
- `bg-[#004299] text-white`
- Hover: `hover:bg-[#012A72]` (darker navy on hover)

### Medium (Secondary)
- `border border-[#004299] text-[#004299]`
- Hover: `hover:bg-[#f7f9fd] hover:border-[#012A72] hover:text-[#012A72]` (outline hover fill — very light; distinct from sidebar `Sidebar BG` `#e7f1f8`)

### Low (Tertiary)
- `bg-[#e7f1f8] text-[#004299]`
- Hover: `hover:bg-[#e7eaf4] hover:text-[#012A72]` (hover fill `#e7eaf4`; distinct from **Offset Weak** `#f5f9fe` used for tables, filters, and rows)

## Sizes

| Size | Padding | Min Width | Text | Height |
|---|---|---|---|---|
| Large | `p-4` | `min-w-[120px]` | `text-[16px] leading-[20px]` | 56px |
| Medium | `px-4 py-2.5` | `min-w-[120px]` | `text-[14px] leading-[20px]` | 40px |
| Small | `px-4 py-2` | `min-w-[80px]` | `text-[12px] leading-[16px]` | 32px |

## States

### Disabled (all emphasis levels)
- `bg-[#ebebeb] text-[#acacac] opacity-64 cursor-not-allowed`

### Loading
- Replace label with animated dots, same container styling

## Icon Variants
- **Leading/Trailing**: icon + label in row, `gap-2`
- **Both**: leading icon + label + trailing icon
- **Only**: square (56×56 / 40×40 / 32×32), icon centered, no label

## Special Buttons
- **"Save & Publish"**: success green `bg-[#21c179] hover:bg-[#1aa866]`
- **"Settle Now"**: small primary `bg-[#004299] text-white text-[12px] px-4 py-2 rounded-[8px]`

## Legacy CTA Pattern
Some older pages use: `bg-[#004299] text-white text-[14px] font-semibold px-6 py-3 rounded-lg hover:bg-[#003377]`. Prefer Button_v2 for new code.
